<i>As I wish</i>
<i>如我所愿 </i>

54
00:03:46,392 --> 00:03:48,436
<i>As you wish</i>
<i>如你所愿</i>

55
00:03:48,436 --> 00:03:52,065
<i>All the days of you and I</i>
<i>我们度过的所有日子</i>

